# Logging Rules

Log:

✓ Admin Login

✓ User Suspension

✓ User Activation

✓ Withdrawal Approval

✓ Withdrawal Rejection

✓ Withdrawal Completion

✓ Settings Changes

---

Never log:

✗ JWT Tokens

✗ Refresh Tokens

✗ Secrets

✗ Full Bank Account Numbers

---

# Performance Rules

Create indexes:

- user_status
- order_status
- withdrawal_status
- audit_created_at

---

All admin lists must:

✓ Paginate

✓ Filter

✓ Sort

---

Never return entire datasets.

